name: The Future Rerun #13 - Dancing Nymphs of Yangmei
description: "Those Nymphs are the built-in ICE that guard databases running YangmeiOS. They move in a mesmerising manner, constantly emitting a sensory disruptive pheromone to lure hackers into a trap which smells like a chunk of valuable data. Once the hacker is in the trap, the four Nymphs would initiate attacking programmes." 800x800px, GIF. Poppel, 2021-07.
